{"tid":2295004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［南丫海難］法庭唔召開死因研訊，搞到家屬連死者嘅死亡證都拎唔到","createTime":"2020-11-21T12:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T16:14:57.000Z","uid":188515,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be53df1d6c172c559e4fd18f5bf8d5725780c928","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:25:55.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】死因裁判官通知南丫海難家屬，指海難死者的死亡原因明確，毋須召開死因研訊。有家屬表示十分憤怒，沒想過會不召開死因庭。協助他們的立法會議員涂謹申表示，死因研訊可讓家屬參與盤問，調查委員會不能取代，希望死因裁判官覆檢決定。<br />\n一場奪去39條人命的海難，家屬多年來爭取召開死因庭，找出親人死亡原因。等了八年終於收到通知，結論是不會召開死因研訊。海難倖存者趙炳全：「很不滿，連死因庭都可以不開。很憤怒，絕對不公平。」<br />\n死因裁判官在信中表示，海難引申的刑事檢控已先後有兩名船長及兩名海事處官員被判罪成，其中海泰號船長誤殺罪成，判囚八年。又指律政司考慮其他證據後，已於上月通知警方不會作出進一步的刑事檢控。死因裁判官認為，由法官倫明高任主席的調查委員會，2013年發表的報告及海難相關的刑事審訊，已全面披露海難死者的死因及死亡的環境情況。死因裁判官考慮相關報告及病理科醫生的遺體剖驗報告後，裁定海難死者是「非法被殺」。<br />\n死因裁判官又指委員會的職權事實上與死因研訊的目的完全重疊，認為委員會作出的建議已涵蓋所有防止相類事故再發生的情況，因此無須召開死因研訊，會將決定通知生死註冊處。<br />\n立法會議員涂謹申：「我仍然有質疑、懷疑，真正撞船原因仍是一個謎，我質疑有人有事沒公開，我覺得是刻意不召開，當局還有很多隱瞞事實不告訴我們。你不召開死因庭，就麻煩你公開你承諾公開的調查報告。」<br />\n一直協助他們的立法會議員涂謹申指，死因裁判官今次作出的結論是一個閉門裁決，而死因研訊亦有特定功能，調查委員會或刑事調查都取代不到。涂謹申：「程序當中死者家屬沒有盤問權利，死者家屬不掌握，不單倫明高法官，還有所有後續法庭程序、相關的文件都不掌握，尤其一些要保密的調查報告都不掌握。所以召開公開、能向公眾問責，向家屬交代最好的真相，給予家屬找出真相的權利最公道。」他希望死因裁判官會再覆檢決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=40513&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D40513%26ct%3D1&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=a7394acb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=40513&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"07f169b3bf7bc956c0c0b1ceac646a9988e0bb41","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42550c1f88491257aad710c04699176a55218faa","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:26:44.000Z","msg":"毋忘港殤日10.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm5lD4qVNNgI&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=b4b2294b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI</a>"},{"pid":"b88ae73d92e8699e875a1d2604a8feba2880f35a","tid":2295004,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:26:44.000Z","msg":"sad"},{"pid":"c8933aeb6960a344348e39804a2cfc61beb0260b","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d78cc4d1eced741bb27a0efc30c5a2972e8f15f","tid":2295004,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d879d7b2355aca459973e8e54f65dd2f1206eb0","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4580bfbdf0c42dcb38f06bf8d99b440d52eb541","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df6c6d6c64a79052a262cb9cbd50737f5ea5d44","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6be3fd7960e1677646e7b52c9aaaa045c70c341","tid":2295004,"uid":229436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"政府:理撚得你咩 我煙花照放呀<br />\n再嘈 我派3萬警隊拉曬你地告你國安法 送你中呀"},{"pid":"3647e6aa7b9f9e47b535f975031b76ff203b8707","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a306b75f1ea0f07acce1e9758eeb223aa511bd0","tid":2295004,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=港共曱甴集團"},{"pid":"2b04ad1c9ea2a35d2175f821e16335451fb31750","tid":2295004,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d10c5e57041754911cbc50a51d052af0b05b809","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29fee4efdd6f866a4542952f8a00bc7396c50e9","tid":2295004,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5f8bfa14b249e1bc3290eca66bfe38f5152175","tid":2295004,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"香港死因裁判官根本係笑話<br />\n當日徐步高個庭根本唔係研判死因,係個官不停指控徐步高點賤格無人性<br />\n類似中國批鬥大會,不過係批鬥無得反駁的死人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>事後該官轉位瘋狂重判社運人士</strong><br />\n這就是D100同大律師公會永遠唔講的事"},{"pid":"270c6c37f9e0a52f06e1f7dd7a1b2c97fe76730f","tid":2295004,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:10:44.000Z","msg":"當日調查委員會的倫明高法官係一九七七年至一九八一年間在<strong>香港前律政署任職</strong><br />\n<br />\n香港政府專搵自己友主持委員會本身已是不當,係咪貪容易指揮?<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>委員會同死因庭功能完全唔同,公民黨做咩唔出聲?<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">要堅持法治依然未死首先就要譴責司法不義而唔係扮盲</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"76d9d9b4f22a044cbe38c01d135c2f507b5e3319","tid":2295004,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"42550c1f88491257aad710c04699176a55218faa","tid":2295004,"uid":188515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T12:26:44.000Z","msg":"毋忘港殤日10.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fm5lD4qVNNgI&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5r3WT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=b4b2294b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/m5lD4qVNNgI</a>"}}